no changes: no recompilation
$ gprbuild -P prj.gpr
update timestamp (now): no recompilation
$ gprbuild -P prj.gpr
update timestamp (past): no recompilation
$ gprbuild -P prj.gpr
change file and update timestamp (past): recompilation
$ gprbuild -P prj.gpr
[C Compile]       toto.c
$ gprclean -P prj.gpr
